      "title": "Four who came to sell jewelry are in the police net",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Monaragala police say that four persons have been arrested for selling 4 gajamuthus in a car in Monaragala city.",
        "According to the information received by the police, they were arrested when this group came to Monaragala city for extortion.",
        "The arrested people are aged 35, 45, 47, and 66, the police said."
      ],
